# MacOS

all samples done with digital color meter and transparency disabled

# dark mode manual sample

1e - menu background on left / control background  / text background
28 - under page background  / alternating content background
2d - menu bar without focus
32 - window background
34 - label4, separator, grid
35..41 - menu bar with focus
38 - tab container background
3e - tab window background
46 - highlighted menu bar item without focus / unemphasized selected text background
55 - label3 / placeholdertext / control / disabled control (text)
6a - inactive buttons
9c - active button without focus
98989d - system gray (maybe active button w/o focus?)
99 - label2
dc - window frame text / selected control text
e3 - label1
ff - selected menu item  / alternate selected menu item  / header / text / selected text / unemphasized selected text


light mode manual sample

menu bar is gradient from e5 to d0

00 - text / selected text
21 - label1
27 - control text /  header text / selected control text / window frame text
80 - label2
8e8e92 - system gray
a1 - under page background / alternating content background
c0 - disabled control (text) / label3 / placeholdertext
cc - grid
da - tab window background
dc - highlighted menu bar item without focus / unemphasized selected text background
e3 - tab container background
e5 - active button without focus
e5..d0 - menu bar with focus
e6 - label4, separator
ec - window background
f6 - menu bar without focus
ff - control color, inactive buttons, menu background on left / control
background color / text background color, selected menu item , alternate selected menu item


